":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"英格蘭如果有個世界級派牌既就真係勁<br />\n<br />\n但阿里同lin都係走位型球員，中場真係冇乜人派得好，之前搵阿里派，得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"太子頂唔頂到？"},{"pid":"283f38135731d16a570c4a781dca3aafd210d3b9","tid":572844,"uid":1734,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:52:33.000Z","msg":"球員幾勁 會員都係垃撚圾 唔死都無用"},{"pid":"d1a842d92ae6b26249bfc5b27352b8c65ad4fa8a","tid":572844,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:53:57.000Z","msg":"用左幾耐寫篇文"},{"pid":"eeaa4bbe84283c21b6b34bd8584fce77191813f2","tid":572844,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"sina on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621e7965c69e6a84df28a192ef5cab304bbf682d","tid":572844,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b0986c891bcb1b98a0bc6931473ffa8bc10739d","tid":572844,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abface958209bf0b61a9e69983d03d0769f0346a","tid":572844,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"英格蘭如果有個世界級派牌既就真係勁<br />\n<br />\n但阿里同lin都係走位型球員，中場真係冇乜人派得好，之前搵阿里派，得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"太子頂唔頂到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"上腳推進一流，但分波未到一線，除非有狗屎運或者突然成熟左，如果唔係都幾難做到大力臣個效果，連加特就執second 波好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 曼班叻架好多時頂贏但頂左去冇人既位，好多人唔識捕，但lin真係幾識執呢啲波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英格蘭巴克利同韋舒亞都係唔夠強，咩軒達臣呢啲已經冇哂當年係黑貓既靈感啦，當年啲派牌幾有潛質"},{"pid":"6c76adde0cdf78d66f4b08031da1f5a26066c046","tid":572844,"uid":50385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"林納爾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881c963e122a3628f1aada8dc1c1c32d7b79539e","tid":572844,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"奧脫福的8萬球迷集體膜拜他。<br />\n奧脫福邊坐到80k人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f9a59ea58ada1ec8ea881d89c29f607773d2bf","tid":572844,"uid":872,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/112701_aedcea18d65c4b08b7c2a76018d3ffaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F112701_aedcea18d65c4b08b7c2a76018d3ffaf.png&h=d712bf19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ad3d6f470abe71e4ba9b091744f7e1af38d7ac1","tid":572844,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/112701_aedcea18d65c4b08b7c2a76018d3ffaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F112701_aedcea18d65c4b08b7c2a76018d3ffaf.png&h=d712bf19&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a80bc2061515f3ce90237b0dc128541bb58085","tid":572844,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88f9a59ea58ada1ec8ea881d89c29f607773d2bf","tid":572844,"uid":872,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/112701_aedcea18d65c4b08b7c2a76018d3ffaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F112701_aedcea18d65c4b08b7c2a76018d3ffaf.png&h=d712bf19&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply